Package me.utk.util.function.void_lambda Description

A package that contains FunctionalInterfaces which represent void lambda functions taking any number of parameters.

For functions with fewer than 10 parameters, there are individual, parametrized classes which can specify the exact types of every argument. The generalized class VoidLambdaN is also available for any functions that require 10 or more parameters as well as for applications which can have varying argument list lengths.

For lambda functions which can return values (as opposed to being void), go to the me.utk.util.function.lambda package instead.
